description:
This is a 36 minute workout called 'A Deep Relaxation Meditation That Will Take You to a New Reality' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is an Original guided meditation recorded by us.  This is a 35 minute guided meditation designed for deep relaxation in a way that transitions you to shift into a new reality.  Today, let us dare to envision a reality that transcends the boundaries of what we perceive as possible, let us carry this vision in our hearts where it may guide our actions, inspire our choices, and ripple outwards, touching the lives of others.  Together, let us weave the fabric of this new reality, one small act of kindness at a time.

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
If you would like to join our monthly supporters, you can do so here:  https://www.buymeacoffee.com/greatmeditation/membership
